headline: Fifth Third Empowers Next Generation with Financial Literacy Solutions
summary: CINCINNATI, November 19, 2024--Extending its longstanding commitment to financial literacy, the Fifth Third Foundation is proud to support the development of a new tool that aims to make personal finance more accessible to young adults.
